title: Colts-Texans TNF Preview (Football 11/21)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jared Dubin to preview Colts-Texans on Thursday Night Football. The guys discuss the impact this game will have on the AFC South race, how injuries could affect this matchup, what we'll see from Jacoby Brissett and Deshaun Watson, if we will see T.Y. Hilton and how Houston's backfield will operate before analyzing player props and picking the game.
